{"word":"H5472 - סוּג - çûwg - soog - Backslider","slug":"H5472","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סוּג</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>çûwg"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soog"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Backslider"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05D2; - su&#x0302;<a href='S:g'>g</a></b> - <i>soog</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>flinch</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>go back</i>, literally (to <i>retreat</i>) or figuratively (to <i>apostatize</i>): - backslider, drive, go back, turn (away, back)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5253\">H5253</a>, <a href=\"#/H5509\">H5509</a>, <a href=\"#/H7734\">H7734</a>, <a href=\"#/H7873\">H7873</a>"}]}